Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.54,1:22:36.90,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}这个世界依然是
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.41,1:22:42.24,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}僕を飼いならしていたいみたいな
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.41,1:22:42.24,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}想要驯服我的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.33,1:22:44.80,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}望み通りだろう?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.33,1:22:44.80,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}那就如你所愿吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.03,1:22:48.44,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}美しくもがくよ
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.03,1:22:48.44,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}我定会　美丽的挣扎
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.92,1:22:52.22,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}互いの砂時計
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.92,1:22:52.22,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}望着彼此的沙漏
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.86,1:22:57.52,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}眺めながらキスをしようよ
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.86,1:22:57.52,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}来温柔的接吻吧
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.59,1:23:04.09,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}『さよなら』から一番　遠い　場所で待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.59,1:23:04.09,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}我们一起到那个　离“告别”最远的地方去吧
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.80,1:23:28.52,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}辞書にある言葉で　出来上がった世界を憎んだ
Dialogue: 0,1:23:20.80,1:23:28.52,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}这个由词典上的语言堆出来的世界　真令人憎恨呐
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.68,1:23:31.25,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}万華鏡の中で
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.68,1:23:31.25,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}在万花筒中
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.61,1:23:34.85,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}八月のある朝
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.61,1:23:34.85,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}在八月的某个清晨
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.45,1:23:38.83,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}君は僕の前で
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.45,1:23:38.83,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}你就在我面前
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.36,1:23:44.02,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}ハニかんでは澄ましてみせた
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.36,1:23:44.02,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}腼腆而又故作镇定地
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.07,1:23:50.27,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}この世界の教科書の　ような笑顔で
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.07,1:23:50.27,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}露出这世上　最标准的笑容
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.36,1:24:09.86,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}ついに時はきた
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.36,1:24:09.86,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}终于是时候了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.30,1:24:14.97,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}昨日までは序章の序章で
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.30,1:24:14.97,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}昨天仅仅只是序章的序章
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.24,1:24:17.56,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}飛ばし読みでいいから
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.24,1:24:17.56,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}前面的内容都可以跳过
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.06,1:24:21.57,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}ここからが僕だよ
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.06,1:24:21.57,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}我从这开始要出场啦
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.97,1:24:25.23,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}経験と知識と
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.97,1:24:25.23,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}带上经验与知识
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.90,1:24:30.52,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}カビの生えかかった勇気を持って
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.90,1:24:30.52,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}还有那已经发霉的勇气
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.75,1:24:34.59,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}未だかつてないスピードで
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.75,1:24:34.59,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}以前所未有的速度
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.61,1:24:36.94,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}君のもとへダイブを
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.61,1:24:36.94,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}冲向你的身边
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.00,1:24:41.86,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}まどろみの中で　生温いコーラに
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.00,1:24:41.86,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}快睡着的时候　我透过微热的可乐
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.95,1:24:45.66,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}ここでないどこかを　夢見たよ
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.95,1:24:45.66,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}仿佛梦到了　某个地方
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.77,1:24:49.41,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}教室の窓の外に
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.77,1:24:49.41,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}那是教室的窗外
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.63,1:24:55.11,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}電車に揺られ　運ばれる朝に
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.63,1:24:55.11,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}那是早晨　颠簸的电车里
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.88,1:30:20.10,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}愛し方さえも
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.88,1:30:20.10,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}连我示爱的方式
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.56,1:30:23.61,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}君の匂いがした
Dialogue: 0,1:30:20.56,1:30:23.61,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}也散发着你的味道
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.70,1:30:27.20,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}歩き方さえも
Dialogue: 0,1:30:24.70,1:30:27.20,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}连我走路的姿势
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.52,1:30:31.44,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}その笑い声がした
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.52,1:30:31.44,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}也传出了你的笑声
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.19,1:30:39.17,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}いつか消えてなくなる　君のすべてを
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.19,1:30:39.17,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}总有一天　你的一切都会消失
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.92,1:30:44.01,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}この眼に焼き付けておくことは
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.92,1:30:44.01,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}所以将你深深的铭刻在这双眼睛上
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.01,1:30:47.04,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}もう権利なんかじゃない
Dialogue: 0,1:30:44.01,1:30:47.04,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}这并不是我的权利
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.72,1:30:52.04,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}義務だと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.72,1:30:52.04,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}而是我的义务啊
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.71,1:31:18.71,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}運命だとか未来とかって　言葉がどれだけ手を
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.71,1:31:18.71,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}命运啊未来啊　这样的词语
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.79,1:31:26.48,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}伸ばそうと届かない　場所で僕ら恋をする
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.79,1:31:26.48,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}让我们到一个　它们传达不到的地方去恋爱
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.64,1:31:34.24,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}時計の針も二人を　横目に見ながら進む
Dialogue: 0,1:31:26.64,1:31:34.24,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}时钟的指针在我们深情对视时　缓缓流逝
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.38,1:31:37.88,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}そんな世界を二人で
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.38,1:31:37.88,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}我们二人就在这样的世界里
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.92,1:31:42.00,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}一生　いや、何章でも
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.92,1:31:42.00,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,150)}一生也好、永世也罢
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.16,1:31:49.38,Lyrics-JB,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,2300)}生き抜いていこう
Dialogue: 0,1:31:42.16,1:31:49.38,Lyrics-CN,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&H5a\fad(150,2300)}坚强的活下去吧
